\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:538:\"<p>Long on our to-do list, we\'re excited to let you know we\'ve introduced the Video Background Addon for SiteOrigin Premium. Transform your websites look with the SiteOrigin Video Background Addon. Introduce dynamic video backgrounds to any Page Builder row, column, or widget, adding an energetic touch to your site.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/add-dynamic-video-backgrounds-to-page-builder/\">Add Dynamic Video Backgrounds to Page Builder</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Aaron Evans\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11751:\"<div id=\"pl-427349\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-427349-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\"  style=\"margin-bottom: 30px\" ><div id=\"pgc-427349-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-427349-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"0\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"\n			\n		>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>Long on our to-do list, we\'re excited to let you know we\'ve introduced the Video Background Addon for SiteOrigin Premium. Transform your websites look with the SiteOrigin Video Background Addon. Introduce dynamic video backgrounds to any Page Builder row, column, or widget, adding an energetic touch to your site. With support for various video formats like mp4, m4v, mov, wmv, avi, mpg, ogv, and webm, flexibility is at your fingertips. The addon goes further by offering semi-transparent overlays or patterns, striking the right balance between the liveliness of videos and the clarity of your text. Its seamless integration with the Page Builder ensures an effortless experience in creating web pages that are both visually captivating and user-friendly.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/video-background/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">View the Video Background Addon demo</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-427349-1\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\"  style=\"margin-bottom: 50px\" ><div id=\"column-background\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-427349-1\" ><div id=\"pgc-427349-1-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell panel-video-background-cover panel-has-overlay\" ><div style=\"padding: 30px 30px 30px 30px;\" class=\"panel-cell-style panel-cell-style-for-427349-1-0\" >				<div\n					class=\"panel-background-overlay\"\n											style=\"\n						background-color:#000000;						\"\n									>\n					<div class=\"so-premium-video-background\" style=\"opacity: 0.7;\"><video autoplay muted playsinline  loop ><source\n						src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/pexels_videos_2110771-720p.mp4\"\n						type=\"video/mp4\"\n					></video></div>				</div>\n				<div id=\"panel-427349-1-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-headline panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"1\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-headline so-widget-sow-headline-default-4dd103cfa2c7-427349\"\n			\n		><div class=\"sow-headline-container \">\n							<h2 class=\"sow-headline\">\n						SHOP MOUNTAIN RANGE						</h2>\n						</div>\n</div></div></div></div><div id=\"pgc-427349-1-1\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell panel-video-background-cover panel-has-overlay\" ><div style=\"padding: 30px 30px 30px 30px;\" class=\"panel-cell-style panel-cell-style-for-427349-1-1\" >				<div\n					class=\"panel-background-overlay\"\n											style=\"\n						background-color:#000000;						\"\n									>\n					<div class=\"so-premium-video-background\" style=\"opacity: 0.7;\"><video autoplay muted playsinline  loop ><source\n						src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/production_id_5193615-720p.mp4\"\n						type=\"video/mp4\"\n					></video></div>				</div>\n				<div id=\"panel-427349-1-1-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-headline panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-headline so-widget-sow-headline-default-4dd103cfa2c7-427349\"\n			\n		><div class=\"sow-headline-container \">\n							<h2 class=\"sow-headline\">\n						SHOP OCEAN RANGE						</h2>\n						</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-427349-2\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-427349-2-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-427349-2-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"\n			\n		>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>Background videos can be added to Page Builder rows, columns, or widgets.</p>\n<p>The following settings will be available when adding a video in the Row, Column, or Widget Design settings section. Only the Background Video setting will initially be visible. Once a background video has been added, the secondary settings will be displayed.</p>\n<p><strong>Background Video</strong><br />\nClick Select Video to add a video from your Media Library or upload a video. Use the External URL field if you\'d like to add an externally hosted background video.</p>\n<p><strong>Background Video Opacity</strong><br />\nAdjust the background video opacity to reveal either the page background color or the row background color. The row background color can be set using the Background Color setting above the Background Video setting.</p>\n<p><strong>Loop Video</strong><br />\nDisable to play the background video once.</p>\n<p><strong>Background Video Display</strong><br />\nChoose between Full (full size) or Cover to cover the available space.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_427272\" style=\"width: 368px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-427272\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/video-bg-settings-358x699.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"358\" height=\"699\" class=\"size-large wp-image-427272\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/video-bg-settings-358x699.png 358w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/video-bg-settings-154x300.png 154w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/video-bg-settings-538x1050.png 538w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/video-bg-settings-313x611.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/video-bg-settings.png 552w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 358px) 100vw, 358px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-427272\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Add a Background Video to your row, column, or widget using the Background Video > Select Video setting or the External URL field.</p></div>\n<h4>Row Background Videos</h4>\n<p>To add a background video to a Page Builder row, insert a new row or editing an existing row by clicking the wrench icon on the right.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_425601\" style=\"width: 1856px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-425601\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/page-builder-edit-row.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1846\" height=\"326\" class=\"size-full wp-image-425601\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/page-builder-edit-row.png 1846w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/page-builder-edit-row-300x53.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/page-builder-edit-row-699x123.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/page-builder-edit-row-768x136.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/page-builder-edit-row-1536x271.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/page-builder-edit-row-1050x185.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/page-builder-edit-row-313x55.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1846px) 100vw, 1846px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-425601\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Click the wrench icon on the right to edit an existing Page Builder row.</p></div>\n<p>Next, open the Design section and click Select Video under the Background Video label or use the External Video field to insert a video URL.</p>\n<h4>Column Background Videos</h4>\n<p>To add a background video to a Page Builder column, insert a new row or editing an existing row by clicking the wrench icon on the right.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Use the Column Count field at the top left of the row edit modal to insert your column count, we\'ve used <code>2</code> in our example below.</li>\n<li>Click on the column you\'d like to edit and a new Column \"X\" Styles panel will appear under Row Styles on the right where \"X\" represents the number of the column you\'ve selected. In our screenshot below, we\'ve selected column <code>1</code>.</li>\n<li>Open the Design settings section and add Background Color, Background Video and adjust the Background Video Opacity as required.</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_427285\" style=\"width: 2770px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-427285\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-column-background-video.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2760\" height=\"1452\" class=\"size-full wp-image-427285\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-column-background-video.png 2760w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-column-background-video-300x158.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-column-background-video-699x368.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-column-background-video-768x404.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-column-background-video-1536x808.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-column-background-video-2048x1077.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-column-background-video-1050x552.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-column-background-video-313x165.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2760px) 100vw, 2760px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-427285\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Select a column, use the Column Styles field on the right to add a video in the Design section.</p></div>\n<h4>Widget Background Videos</h4>\n<p>To a video to a widget, edit a widget by clicking on the widget or hovering over the widget and clicking the Edit link. Under Widget Styles on the right, open the Design section and click Select Video under the Background Video label or use the External Video field to insert a video URL.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_427297\" style=\"width: 2770px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-427297\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-widget-background-video.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2760\" height=\"1328\" class=\"size-full wp-image-427297\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-widget-background-video.png 2760w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-widget-background-video-300x144.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-widget-background-video-699x336.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-widget-background-video-768x370.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-widget-background-video-1536x739.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-widget-background-video-2048x985.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-widget-background-video-1050x505.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/page-builder-widget-background-video-313x151.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2760px) 100vw, 2760px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-427297\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Edit a widget, open Widget Styles > Design on the right and click Select Video under the Background Video label.</p></div>\n<h4>Wrap Up</h4>\n<p>Thanks for reading, we\'re excited to see the layouts you create with the Video Background Addon. Please let us know if we can assist in any way. If you aren\'t using SiteOrigin Premium and are interested in what else is on offer, head on over to the <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">SiteOrigin Premium product page</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div><p>The post <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/add-dynamic-video-backgrounds-to-page-builder/\">Add Dynamic Video Backgrounds to Page Builder</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://siteorigin.com/add-dynamic-video-backgrounds-to-page-builder/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"Copy Paste Page Builder Content Between Sites\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://siteorigin.com/copy-paste-page-builder-content-between-sites/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://siteorigin.com/copy-paste-page-builder-content-between-sites/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 02 Oct 2023 19:37:12 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=417968\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:536:\"<p>Speed up your building process by copying Page Builder rows and widgets between websites with the SiteOrigin Premium Cross Domain Copy Paste Addon. The Cross Domain Copy Paste Addon offers two methods of moving your Page Builder content between websites, the Browser Clipboard Method and the Browser Storage Method.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/copy-paste-page-builder-content-between-sites/\">Copy Paste Page Builder Content Between Sites</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Aaron Evans\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12089:\"<p>Speed up your building process by copying Page Builder rows and widgets between websites with the SiteOrigin Premium Cross Domain Copy Paste Addon.</p>\n<p>The Cross Domain Copy Paste Addon offers two methods of moving your Page Builder content between websites, the Browser Clipboard Method and the Browser Storage Method. The Browser Clipboard Method is the simplest option. The Browser Storage Method offers a quicker workflow but is reliant on browser permissions which can be tricky to setup in some instances. Let&#8217;s take a look at how each method works.</p>\n<p>Choose your copy paste method from <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Cross Domain Copy Paste</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Settings</span></span>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_417983\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-417983\" class=\"size-large wp-image-417983\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cross-domain-copy-paste-settings-1-699x475.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"475\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cross-domain-copy-paste-settings-1-699x475.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cross-domain-copy-paste-settings-1-300x204.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cross-domain-copy-paste-settings-1-768x522.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cross-domain-copy-paste-settings-1-1050x713.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cross-domain-copy-paste-settings-1-313x213.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/cross-domain-copy-paste-settings-1.png 1446w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-417983\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Choose your Copy Paste method from SiteOrigin &gt; Premium Addons &gt; Cross Domain Copy Paste &gt; Settings.</p></div>\n<h3>Browser Clipboard Method</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Right-click on a Page Builder <strong>source</strong> row or widget, click Copy Row or Copy Widget.</li>\n<li>Go to your <strong>destination</strong> page, locate the Cross Domain Copy Paste field below the content area, right-click, and Paste your data.</li>\n<li>Finally, right-click within Page Builder and select Paste Row or Paste Widget from the contextual menu.</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_418230\" style=\"width: 1906px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-418230\" class=\"size-full wp-image-418230\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1896\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu.png 1896w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-300x192.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-699x448.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-768x492.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-1536x983.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-1050x672.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-313x200.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1896px) 100vw, 1896px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-418230\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Right-click in Page Builder and click Copy Widget or Copy Row.</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_419207\" style=\"width: 1896px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-419207\" class=\"wp-image-419207 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/browser-clipboard-metabox-pasted.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1886\" height=\"628\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/browser-clipboard-metabox-pasted.png 1886w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/browser-clipboard-metabox-pasted-300x100.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/browser-clipboard-metabox-pasted-699x233.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/browser-clipboard-metabox-pasted-768x256.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/browser-clipboard-metabox-pasted-1536x511.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/browser-clipboard-metabox-pasted-1050x350.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/browser-clipboard-metabox-pasted-313x104.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1886px) 100vw, 1886px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-419207\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Go to your destination page, locate the Cross Domain Copy Paste field below the content area, right-click, and Paste your data.</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_419216\" style=\"width: 1905px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-419216\" class=\"wp-image-419216 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1895\" height=\"605\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget.png 1895w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-300x96.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-699x223.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-768x245.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-1536x490.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-1050x335.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-313x100.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1895px) 100vw, 1895px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-419216\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Finally, right-click within Page Builder and select Paste Row or Paste Widget from the contextual menu.</p></div>\n<h3>Browser Storage Method</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>At <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Cross Domain Copy Paste: Settings</span></span>Click the Grant Permission button conditionally displayed below the Browser Storage radio button.</li>\n<li>Grant permissions on both the <strong>source</strong> and <strong>destination</strong> websites.</li>\n<li>Right-click on a Page Builder <strong>source</strong> row or widget, click Copy Row or Copy Widget.</li>\n<li>Go to your <strong>destination</strong> page, right-click in Page Builder, and click Paste Row or Paste Widget.</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_419292\" style=\"width: 214px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-419292\" class=\"wp-image-419292 size-medium\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/grant-permissions-button-300x206.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"206\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/grant-permissions-button-300x206.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/grant-permissions-button-313x215.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/grant-permissions-button.png 359w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-419292\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Click the Grant Permission button.</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_419293\" style=\"width: 542px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-419293\" class=\"wp-image-419293 size-large\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cross-domain-consent-modal-632x699.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"632\" height=\"699\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cross-domain-consent-modal-632x699.png 632w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cross-domain-consent-modal-271x300.png 271w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cross-domain-consent-modal-768x849.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cross-domain-consent-modal-950x1050.png 950w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cross-domain-consent-modal-313x346.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/cross-domain-consent-modal.png 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 632px) 100vw, 632px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-419293\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Grant permissions on both the <strong>source</strong> and <strong>destination</strong> websites.</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_418230\" style=\"width: 1906px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-418230\" class=\"wp-image-418230 size-full\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1896\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu.png 1896w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-300x192.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-699x448.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-768x492.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-1536x983.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-1050x672.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/page-builder-right-click-contextual-menu-313x200.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1896px) 100vw, 1896px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-418230\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Right-click in Page Builder and click Copy Widget or Copy Row.</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_419216\" style=\"width: 1905px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-419216\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1895\" height=\"605\" class=\"size-full wp-image-419216\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget.png 1895w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-300x96.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-699x223.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-768x245.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-1536x490.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-1050x335.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/contextual-menu-paste-widget-313x100.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1895px) 100vw, 1895px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-419216\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Finally, right-click within Page Builder and select Paste Row or Paste Widget from the contextual menu.</p></div>\n<h4>Wrap Up</h4>\n<p>Thanks for reading, we hope you find the Cross Domain Copy Paste Addon speeds up your workflow. Please let us know if we can assist in any way. If you aren&#8217;t using SiteOrigin Premium and are interested in what else is on offer, head on over to the <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">SiteOrigin Premium product page</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/copy-paste-page-builder-content-between-sites/\">Copy Paste Page Builder Content Between Sites</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://siteorigin.com/copy-paste-page-builder-content-between-sites/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"Get Creative With Custom Image Shapes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"htt