it\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5638:\"<div id=\"pl-415146\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-415146-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-no-style\" ><div id=\"pgc-415146-0-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\" ><div id=\"panel-415146-0-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-first-child\" data-index=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"\n			\n		>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<p>Remember those cool image shapes we added in July? Well, we\'ve just pumped up the volume with our <strong>SiteOrigin Premium Image Shape Addon</strong>. More shapes, more effects, more fun!</p>\n<h3>What\'s New?</h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_415165\" style=\"width: 3016px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-415165\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/so-premium-custom-shapes.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"3006\" height=\"1371\" class=\"size-full wp-image-415165\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/so-premium-custom-shapes.png 3006w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/so-premium-custom-shapes-300x137.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/so-premium-custom-shapes-699x319.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/so-premium-custom-shapes-768x350.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/so-premium-custom-shapes-1536x701.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/so-premium-custom-shapes-2048x934.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/so-premium-custom-shapes-1050x479.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/so-premium-custom-shapes-313x143.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3006px) 100vw, 3006px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-415165\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">SiteOrigin Premium Custom Shapes</p></div>\n<ul>\n<li>13 new shapes including the Decagon, Arrows, Trapezoid, and more.</li>\n<li>Get artsy with <strong>30 custom blob shapes</strong>.</li>\n<li>Feeling creative? Use the Custom Image Shape feature and turn any image into a shape with your own PNG or SVG.</li>\n<li>Shadows & Effects? We Got \'Em!: Spruce up your images with awesome shadow effects. Control color, blur, spread, and even add hover effects.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Let\'s Get Rolling</h4>\n<p>To dive in:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Make sure you\'ve got the SiteOrigin Premium Plugin and Widgets Bundle Plugin.</li>\n<li>Head over to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Plugins</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin Widgets</span></span>, activate the Image Widget</li>\n<li>Finally, activate the Image Shape Addon at <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Image Shape</span></span>.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div></div><div id=\"panel-415146-0-0-1\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-image\" data-index=\"1\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-image so-widget-sow-image-default-5ba3f87dfe76-415146\"\n			\n		>\n\n<div class=\"sow-image-container\">\n		<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/joel-muniz-E6ExxeQNiN4-unsplash-1050x700.jpg\" width=\"820\" height=\"547\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/joel-muniz-E6ExxeQNiN4-unsplash-1050x700.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/joel-muniz-E6ExxeQNiN4-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/joel-muniz-E6ExxeQNiN4-unsplash-699x466.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/joel-muniz-E6ExxeQNiN4-unsplash-768x512.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/joel-muniz-E6ExxeQNiN4-unsplash-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/joel-muniz-E6ExxeQNiN4-unsplash-313x209.jpg 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/joel-muniz-E6ExxeQNiN4-unsplash-720x480.jpg 720w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/joel-muniz-E6ExxeQNiN4-unsplash-272x182.jpg 272w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/joel-muniz-E6ExxeQNiN4-unsplash.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 820px) 100vw, 820px\" alt=\"\" 		class=\"so-widget-image\"/>\n	</div>\n\n</div></div><div id=\"panel-415146-0-0-2\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_sow-editor panel-last-child\" data-index=\"2\" ><div\n			\n			class=\"so-widget-sow-editor so-widget-sow-editor-base\"\n			\n		>\n<div class=\"siteorigin-widget-tinymce textwidget\">\n	<h4>Wrap Up</h4>\n<p>We\'re stoked about these additions and can\'t wait to see what you\'ll create. Need some guidance?</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/image-widget/\">SiteOrigin Image Widget documentation</a>\n	</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/image-shape/\">SiteOrigin Image Shape Addon documentation</a>.\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Got thoughts or questions? Drop \'em below. Cheers to creating awesome stuff together! <img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f942.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f3a8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /></p>\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div><p>The post <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/get-creative-with-custom-image-shapes/\">Get Creative With Custom Image Shapes</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8