(69, 1, '2024-03-31 18:31:39', '2024-03-31 18:31:39', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>What are the latest trends in mobile app development? Which app development trends will be mainstream in 2024? What is the future of mobile application development?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Find answers to all these questions in this comprehensive write-up on the latest app development trends in 2024.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mobile devices and apps in it are developing at a very rapid pace, and everyone is working on their apps to make them user-friendly. With more and more businesses going digital every day, it is very necessary to keep up with the latest trends to grow in the market.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By the end of 2023, mobile market revenue will cross 700 billion USD. Mobile apps are taking the space of websites, and in the coming time, it will be a sure thing that every business has its own app.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":70,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/blog-website/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/mobile-app-development-trends-latest.jpg\" alt=\"Mobile apps\" class=\"wp-image-70\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>More people are using mobile applications, and an average user spends more than 90 percent of the time on the apps. It brings changes in the user experience on a regular basis, and many app developers are working on improvements.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are more than 50 lakh apps available, and it is growing each day. More than 90% of time spent on mobile devices is on apps, and it is not slowing down. Everyone got attached to the digital world during the pandemic, and apps became the new normal.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It is one of the most tren